&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;8+ years industry experience&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Bachelor’s and/or Master’s degree, preferably in CS, or equivalent experience.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Metrics-driven approach to decision-making, with a track record for delivering quantifiable impact and presenting to engineering leadership.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Expertise in Bazel, and concepts such as action graph, dependency analysis, remote caching.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
