&lt;li&gt;Exceptional ability to translate complex analytical findings into clear, compelling narratives for senior business audiences—you can make a country GM or a VP act on what you&#39;ve built&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven track record of operating with autonomy in fast-moving, ambiguous environments and delivering high-quality work across multiple concurrent priorities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborative, low-ego working style with a strong orientation toward enabling the people around you—we measure success by the decisions our work influences, not the analyses we produce&lt;/li&gt;
