&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;&quot;&gt;As a Senior Release Manager, you will play a critical role in ensuring the successful launch of Internal software to CS agents across the globe.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
