&lt;p&gt;The Homes team is responsible for growing Airbnb’s destination business and growing the supply ensuring we maintain a competitive portfolio of Accommodation listings that meet guest expectations for value, variety, and experience. The team also supports hosts globally by enabling efficient planning and execution of growth strategies that align with Airbnb’s mission and resonate with local communities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Difference You Will Make:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this role, you will report to the Asia Pacific Head of Homes and shape the growth and performance of Airbnb’s Homes business across Southeast Asia Leading a&amp;nbsp; team of high caliber Market Managers across the region, You’ll drive strategies that expand high-quality supply, strengthen host success across every segment, and enhance the guest experience. and set Through close collaboration with cross-functional partners, such as Global Markets, Policy, Legal and Comms&amp;nbsp; you’ll ensure Airbnb continues to deliver exceptional value to both guests and hosts in every market.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A Typical Day:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead and inspire a team of Account Managers to grow Airbnb’s Homes and Hotel business across Southeast Asia, expanding partnerships with hosts of all types and driving exceptional business and guest outcomes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead a team of Acquisition Managers and Vendors to increase the supply of high quality accommodations&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build Destination Southeast Asia strategies to grow the destination business directing teams to tailor their approach based on market maturity and host segmentation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and execute acquisition strategies to bring new, high-quality supply to Airbnb by developing innovative programs, pilots, and local initiatives to reach untapped segments and markets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experiment boldly to unlock new sources of supply - measure results, refine quickly, and turn proven strategies into playbooks that fuel Airbnb’s growth across Southeast Asia&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate cross-functionally with Global Markets, Marketing, RevOps, Policy, and Product to launch initiatives that improve host performance and accelerate destination growth&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor and own business performance, ensuring markets meet revenue, supply, and quality KPIs while delivering sustainable results that support Airbnb’s broader goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify market trends and opportunities, providing solutions to overcome barriers and capitalize on emerging demand or regulatory shifts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coach and develop talent, building a high-performing team culture that values experimentation, accountability, and continuous growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Expertise:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;15+ years of experience, in Commercial roles, Strategy, global operations, business development or marketplace management.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Industry experience in tech, FMCG or Travel&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;At least 5+ years in a people-leadership role managing and scaling teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Expertise and strong understanding of the Regulated Markets n tech industry.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in Management Consulting is a plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analytical and strategic thinker who uses data and insights to uncover opportunities, shape portfolio strategies, and guide decisions across diverse and evolving markets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A combination of operational and commercial skills that will allow you to acquire supply across multiple channels.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A bold, compassionate, and action-oriented leader with a &lt;em&gt;strong bias for action&lt;/em&gt; and a proven ability to develop, coach, and empower high-performing teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven ability to influence product, policy, and cross-functional teams to unlock new revenue streams and improve host and market performance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Skilled at leveraging tools, dashboards, and analytics to assess performance, identify trends, and drive accountability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated success in achieving strong results through others, including effective performance management and development of emerging leaders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Known for creating a positive, driven, and inclusive team culture grounded in collaboration, transparency, and continuous improvement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Recognized as a go-to leader who provides clear direction, constructive feedback, and hands-on business coaching to drive both results and professional growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Highly organized and adept at leading multiple initiatives simultaneously, turning strategy into action and results.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Previous experience&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;growing supply and building partnerships &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;is highly valued.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
