&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Airbnb was born in 2007 when two hosts welcomed three guests to their San Francisco home, and has since grown to over 5 million hosts who have welcomed over 2 billion guest arrivals in almost every country across the globe. Every day, hosts offer unique stays and experiences that make it possible for guests to connect with communities in a more authentic way.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Community You Will Join:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;At Airbnb, quality is not a gate — it’s a platform.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Quality Platform team is reimagining how software is built, tested, and shipped at scale. We sit at the intersection of &lt;strong&gt;Infrastructure, Developer Experience, and Applied AI&lt;/strong&gt;, building the systems that enable thousands of engineers across Airbnb to ship high-quality software with speed and total confidence. &lt;strong&gt;We don’t just find bugs — we build the infrastructure that prevents them.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a cornerstone of Airbnb’s &lt;strong&gt;Engineering Hub in Brazil&lt;/strong&gt;, this team plays a key role in expanding our global platform capabilities while building a high-impact local engineering presence. You will join at a defining moment, helping to shape both the technical direction of the platform and the culture of the Brazil hub.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Difference You Will Make:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As an Engineering Manager, you will lead the vision and execution of Airbnb’s &lt;strong&gt;Full-Cycle Testing Platform.&lt;/strong&gt;Your mission is to move beyond traditional testing silos by building a comprehensive suite of tools that support the entire development lifecycle—from &lt;strong&gt;&quot;Shift-Left&quot;&lt;/strong&gt; early validation and unit testing to high-scale, distributed &lt;strong&gt;End-to-End (E2E) automation.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be a technical leader and a people leader, serving as a &lt;strong&gt;force multiplier&lt;/strong&gt; for engineering teams across Airbnb’s global ecosystem. You will drive the transition to an AI-native quality model, ensuring that quality is intrinsic to every step of the developer journey.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;In this role, you will:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lead a High-Impact Team:&lt;/strong&gt; Build and grow a world-class team of engineers. Foster a culture of &lt;strong&gt;Engineering Craft&lt;/strong&gt;, ownership, and operational excellence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Drive Full-Cycle Platform Strategy:&lt;/strong&gt; Define the roadmap for a unified quality platform that integrates Shift-Left methodologies with robust E2E automation, ensuring high-fidelity signals at every stage.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Transform Quality with AI:&lt;/strong&gt; Lead the adoption of AI-native approaches, leveraging LLMs for autonomous test discovery, predictive failure analysis, and self-healing E2E automation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Champion &quot;Quality by Design&quot;:&lt;/strong&gt; Influence how large-scale systems are built across Airbnb, ensuring that testability, modularity, and scalability are fundamental parts of our global architecture.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Scale the Brazil Hub:&lt;/strong&gt; Partner with the Brazil Site Lead and global leaders to establish operational rhythms, mentor talent, and build the Airbnb engineering brand in the region.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A Typical Day:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategic Leadership:&lt;/strong&gt; Review technical designs and partner with tech leads to ensure our platform provides &lt;strong&gt;early feedback&lt;/strong&gt; to developers while maintaining &lt;strong&gt;comprehensive E2E coverage.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;People &amp;amp; Culture:&lt;/strong&gt; Coach and mentor engineers, driving career growth and fostering an inclusive team environment built on trust and belonging.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Operational Excellence:&lt;/strong&gt; Identify and resolve systemic bottlenecks in our CI/CD pipelines and testing environments to improve developer velocity and release confidence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cross-Functional Influence:&lt;/strong&gt; Collaborate with global Infrastructure, Product, and Data leaders to promote full-cycle quality standards and align on shared technical priorities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategic Sourcing:&lt;/strong&gt; Participate in recruiting, onboarding, and community-building efforts to scale our presence in the Brazil market.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Expertise:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Leadership Mastery:&lt;/strong&gt; 3+ years of engineering management and 7+ years in software engineering, with a proven track record of leading high-performing teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Platform &amp;amp; Infrastructure Mindset:&lt;/strong&gt; Deep experience building or leading infrastructure, developer tooling, or large-scale distributed systems that serve internal engineering customers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Full-Cycle Testing Knowledge:&lt;/strong&gt; A strong understanding of the entire testing pyramid, including unit, integration, and high-scale E2E automation frameworks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategic Execution:&lt;/strong&gt; Demonstrated ability to lead through ambiguity and drive complex technical strategies across geographic and organizational boundaries.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Global Collaboration:&lt;/strong&gt; Exceptional communication skills in English, with the ability to influence technical roadmaps and stakeholders across the globe. (Portuguese is a plus).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technical Pluses:&lt;/strong&gt; Experience with &lt;strong&gt;Mobile Development (iOS/Android)&lt;/strong&gt; or &lt;strong&gt;Applied AI/ML&lt;/strong&gt; is highly valued but not required.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Commitment to Craft:&lt;/strong&gt; A passion for engineering excellence and a curiosity for how AI can redefine the relationship between speed and quality.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our Commitment To Inclusion &amp;amp; Belonging:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;&quot;&gt;Airbnb is committed to working with the broadest talent pool possible. We believe diverse ideas foster innovation and engagement, and allow us to attract creatively-led people, and to develop the best products, services and solutions. All qualified individuals are encouraged to apply.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
