&lt;li&gt;Run Marketing&#39;s core planning cycles end-to-end — annual functional review, quarterly re-planning, quarterly/monthly business reviews, budget management and headcount planning&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with partner teams across sales, product and more to ensure tight alignment on priorities and regular and clear communication&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver data-driven insights and analytics by synthesizing quantitative and qualitative inputs into actionable strategies and business recommendations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with marketing leadership on implementing our teamwide AI transformation strategy, scaling workflows that have already shown value and identifying new use cases across teams&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
