&lt;li&gt;Strong executive presence with experience influencing senior stakeholders, and facilitating senior-level meetings, workshops, and cross-functional forums&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional written and verbal communication skills, with experience crafting clear, compelling narratives for executive audiences&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong analytical skills, with the ability to translate complex data into insights and actionable recommendations (experience with spreadsheets; SQL a plus)&lt;/li&gt;
