&lt;li&gt;Diagnose where reps and managers need the most support across pipeline generation, deal progression, and deal execution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Adapt and regionalize global programs, content, and frameworks for the Japan market, balancing consistency with local relevance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build repeatable sales motions, processes, playbooks, and manager-facing tools that help the field execute more effectively&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Produce, curate, and maintain enablement content and assets that reflect regional priorities and market nuance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Program manage ongoing sales trainings and enablement initiatives across Japan&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Facilitate effective in-person and virtual training sessions, workshops, and deal-based enablement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Measure the effectiveness of priority programs and selling motions to identify what is working and where changes are needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;section page-centered&quot;&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;We&#39;d love to hear from you if you have:&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;6+ years of experience in sales enablement, field enablement, sales strategy, product marketing, or similar field-facing GTM roles&lt;/li&gt;
