&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li1&quot;&gt;Lead a team of motivated and diverse individuals to foster an environment of success&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li1&quot;&gt;Participate in customer and prospect meetings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li1&quot;&gt;Assist in continual training and development, including mentorship, hiring, and career growth&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li1&quot;&gt;Help shape and further develop sales processes and initiatives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li1&quot;&gt;Interview, hire, and train new team members as we scale the business and company&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li1&quot;&gt;Deliver weekly forecast meetings and advise Account Executives on strategies to help exceed their goal&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
