&lt;li&gt;Navigate long, complex sales cycles, including compliance, procurement, and regulatory considerations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with cross-functional teams to position Figma effectively, drive deal progression and ensure successful adoption and expansion&lt;/li&gt;
