&lt;p&gt;Figma is looking for a Product Marketing Manager, Monetization to help shape how teams buy, adopt, and scale Figma. In this role, you&#39;ll be the marketing partner to our Product Growth and Monetization teams, owning go-to-market strategy and customer communications for updates related to our billing model and plans. You&#39;ll also support our Organization and Enterprise selling motions, bringing new admin and governance features to market and equipping sales with the resources, enablement, and processes to win and grow key accounts. If you have a knack for distilling complex product changes into clear, structured communications, or you&#39;re excited about helping the world&#39;s largest companies get the most out of Figma, this role is for you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a full time role that can be held from one of our US hubs or remotely in the United States.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
