&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re growing and moving fast. Our next team member will have an agile, dynamic approach, be comfortable embracing change, a true team-player, and love working with our growing footprint of Fortune 1000 customers. You won’t be alone! Figma has an incredible team and you’ll work closely with other groups including Support, Design, Engineering, Product Marketing, Customer Success, and Community. As a Manager, Mid-Market Sales, you will lead a team of Account Executives responsible for continuing the growth of our Enterprise product. You will report to the Senior Manager, Enterprise Sales.&lt;/p&gt;
