&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;A track record of launching and scaling programs and/or products in new markets from 0 to 1&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Education industry experience, with knowledge of K-12, higher ed, and/or bootcamp landscapes, personas and adoption&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Demonstrated ability to build and manage relationships with government bodies, school leaders, and industry partners across multiple regions&lt;/li&gt;
