&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An affinity for Figma and an interest in becoming an expert in our product&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Previous experience supporting technical or AI focused teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
