&lt;p&gt;This is an exciting opportunity to join an emerging team at Figma where you will play an active role in shaping our long-term partner strategy. You will build new partner programs from scratch and scale our existing motions to new customers and partners across APAC.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
