&lt;p&gt;Examples of accommodations include but are not limited to:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Holding interviews in an accessible location&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enabling closed captioning on video conferencing&lt;/li&gt;
